Text: Yep! I also kind of feel that way when I'm watching mukbangs

Author: Sea_Plane
Text: I've had the occasional inappropriate thought about lasagna...  I feel like when I'm an old lady with dementia in a nursing home, they'll catch me doing all kinds of weird shit with food. I made my friend promise to push me off a cliff when I start losing my mind. Just to spare my family from the embarrassment.
